HEADWORD: rotgut
<hw>rot"gut</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Bad small
beer.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any bad spirituous liquor, especially when
adulterated so as to be very deleterious.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rother</ent>⟦br⟧
